						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of the Vignēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1466, Krōdhi, Jyēshṭa, ba. 30,</hi> corresponding to 1544 A.D., June 20, Friday.</p>						

						<p>Much damaged. It registers remission of certain taxes on the barbers of Kandanavōlu.</p>						

